  "name": "RPlog_A_Meeting_with_Dillon_in_Cafe_Abbatoir",
  "title": "A Meeting with Dillon in Cafe Abattoir",
  "summary": "On Etti IV, Corporate Sector Authority VicePrex Simone Drake -- here using the name Piper -- meets Executive Officer Dillon at the exclusive Cafe Abattoir to discuss the abrupt end of their stay on Caspar. She reports coldly that Dillon's young aide Kuxli endangered the Authority's image by consorting with enemies and Imperial agents and then fled the Espo guards she had assigned to watch him, prompting her to bring him back to Etti IV. Dillon, who took the orphaned Kuxli in to give him guidance, accepts responsibility and promises to discipline the boy once events allow. When Piper mentions her tense run-in with Chewbacca, who had returned to Etti IV and confronted her over Kuxli's removal, an infuriated Dillon abruptly excuses himself to deal with the Wookiee. Piper finishes the meeting, leaves the cafe, collects her waiting dog Duke, and heads home.",
